{"tid":2058494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宣揚香港民族","createTime":"2020-06-10T08:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T04:14:52.000Z","uid":241171,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de3a4494c5dc4008e37d118d0a8722911c559a8e","tid":2058494,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"黎到而家 最驚既係中共同外國傾好數 無得攬炒<br />\n<br />\n既然攬炒就要做到底 唔可以比中共做完野 又無後果<br />\n<br />\n下一步宣揚 香港民族 迫中共攬炒食屎狗 等攬炒黎得更徹底<br />\n要注意 中共既行為完全反應左 佢係寧願香港變廢墟都在所不惜(強推國安法 唔經本地立法)<br />\n所以香港遲早比大陸陰乾 既然係咁就要加速搞到中共惱羞成怒 做盡柒事 <br />\n<br />\n香港唔係大陸人<br />\n<br />\n我地有不同護照<br />\n我地有不同語言<br />\n我地有不同文化<br />\n我地有不同認證<br />\n兩地過境需要過關<br />\n<br />\n大陸會貪污<br />\n大陸有假奶粉<br />\n大陸有豆腐渣<br />\n大陸食狗肉<br />\n大陸死了李旺陽 劉曉波<br />\n大陸是邪惡的食屎狗<br />\n最好全國剷"},{"pid":"0b8ccc95cffd2f23dbc307b966f4ba935744d6b2","tid":2058494,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afe9644fdb8fd331b130c5eb1da3b818c1f3fe5","tid":2058494,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"宣揚香港民族 被政治迫害"},{"pid":"b5640c634490d4386a8ff37faaf7ddb145d3eaba","tid":2058494,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92372721328aa4813f0fb51ce964c7a4bedb48d6","tid":2058494,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02167f6d22c4c05b426f73944a4e3eb6d7fa986d","tid":2058494,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20c084db116462660a4e11a6b1c7329fcf4dd56","tid":2058494,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,